cisc275.group3.model.sceneobject

Class BetaPerson

  • java.lang.Object
    • cisc275.group3.model.sceneobject.SceneObject
      • cisc275.group3.model.sceneobject.BetaPerson
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ActionMove, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<SceneObject>

    public class BetaPerson
extends SceneObject
implements ActionMove
    Beta release mock-up for person. Handles its move behaviors based on the status int. (1- means moving right to left, 0- means stopped until mission is completed and -1 means leaving the screen).

    BetaPerson.java

    Author:
    Jon
